                  <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">Managers</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">supervisors</ENAMEX>: This <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">group</ENAMEX> includes anyone with hiring,
<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">firing</ENAMEX>, disciplinary, or compensatory authority over other <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">workers</ENAMEX>. They are
viewed as <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">employers</ENAMEX>, not <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">employees</ENAMEX>.

               
                  Independent <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">contractors</ENAMEX>: These are <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">people</ENAMEX> who are hired on an
