<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">workforce</ENAMEX>, particularly in computer-related fields.

               
                  <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Agricultural</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">workers</ENAMEX>: Because they are seasonal <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">laborers</ENAMEX> and have a
