                  Domestic <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">employees</ENAMEX>: This <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">group</ENAMEX> includes maids, <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">butlers</ENAMEX>, and other
live-in household help.

            

